 style="width: 53pt;">　</td><td class="xl6711435" width="70" style="width: 53pt;">　</td><td class="xl6611435">　</td><td class="xl6411435"></td></tr><tr height="144" style="height: 108pt;"><td height="144" class="xl6411435" style="height: 108pt;"></td><td class="xl6811435">　</td><td colspan="8" class="xl7111435" width="560" style="width: 424pt;">기업(판매자-리스이용자)이 다른
